text: Jessica Louise Nelson (born 14 June 1991), also known as Jesy Nelson, is a singer-songwriter from England. She was a member of the girl band Little Mix. She went solo in December 2020. She released a song named Boyz feat. Nicki Minaj. She is working on new music.
